title: New QGIS Map Gallery
content: QGIS has a new map gallery! We are looking for submissions of beautiful maps made using QGIS. The maps will be displayed on the main web site at https://qgis.org if approved. Our goal is to show off the power and versatility of QGIS to the world. If you have a great map to share, double click this article to visit the gallery and start sharing your submissions!
